1
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:46,000
[Breaking the Shadows]

2
00:01:46,370 --> 00:01:48,910
[Episode 5]

3
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,710
What are you looking at?

4
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,139
You startled me.

5
00:02:09,210 --> 00:02:10,850
I'm listening to an audiobook.

6
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,610
It's an ongoing series. I've been listening to it.

7
00:02:12,690 --> 00:02:14,510
The killer just went upstairs with a knife, about to murder someone,

8
00:02:14,530 --> 00:02:15,520
and you suddenly...

9
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:16,790
You scared me to death.

10
00:02:17,090 --> 00:02:19,240
You brought me tea leaves again, and so much of it?

11
00:02:19,270 --> 00:02:20,720
I've labeled them for you.

12
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:21,880
Don't mix them up.

13
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,230
Xueman,

14
00:02:24,510 --> 00:02:27,010
you don't have to always bring me such good tea leaves.

15
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,230
The people in our team

16
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:29,430
don't know how to appreciate tea at all.

17
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,520
They're all wasted.

18
00:02:30,829 --> 00:02:32,329
I think you're being inconsiderate.

19
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:33,829
Don't worry about whether they drink or not,

20
00:02:33,829 --> 00:02:35,510
it's a matter of courtesy.

21
00:02:35,579 --> 00:02:36,550
Your job isn't something

22
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:37,710
you can do alone.

23
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:39,590
You'll need others' help someday.

24
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:41,990
I made you some duck soup for reducing internal heat.

25
00:02:42,020 --> 00:02:44,390
Are you going to drink it in front of me,

26
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,840
or pour it out after I leave?

27
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:47,260
I'll drink it. I definitely will.

28
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,630
I promise to finish every last drop.

29
00:02:50,650 --> 00:02:52,520
You're quite busy yourself, Xueman.

30
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:54,460
You don't need to always come take care of me. It's too much trouble.

31
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:55,660
It's not troublesome.

32
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:56,960
You're my only younger sister,

33
00:02:56,990 --> 00:02:58,020
and I'm your only elder sister.

34
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:00,570
Alright.

35
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,220
Go to bed early.

36
00:03:02,410 --> 00:03:03,340
I'll get going now.

37
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:05,140
Don't be late tomorrow.

38
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:06,510
Where are you going?

39
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:09,510
Did you forget?

40
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:11,340
It's Dad and Auntie's death anniversary.

41
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:14,860
I saved it in my reminders.

42
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:15,810
Look,

43
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,650
the alarm hasn't gone off yet.

44
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,260
I never need an alarm.

45
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,230
Every year at this time,

46
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,810
Dad would appear in my dreams.

47
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:25,170
In the past couple of years,

48
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:27,150
he always looks like he's hesitating to say something.

49
00:03:27,670 --> 00:03:29,060
I know what he wants to say.

50
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,200
He thinks

51
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,910
I haven't been taking good care of you.

52
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,230
Han Qing,

53
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,700
please don't think I'm nagging you.

54
00:03:39,730 --> 00:03:41,430
See, girls at your age,

55
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:43,560
are usually finding someone to date,

56
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,829
have children with, get married to,

57
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:46,130
and live a normal life together.

58
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,810
But you are just doing this job.

59
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,829
I'm really afraid that one day you'll end up like Zhong Wei.

60
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:50,860
End up how?

61
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,220
End up dead.

62
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,480
You also think Zhong Wei is dead, don't you?

63
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,590
Remember to drink the soup.

64
00:04:19,329 --> 00:04:20,459
When we got married,

65
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,180
you only told me you were divorced,

66
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:24,290
you didn't mention you had such a grown child.

67
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:26,870
Han Weiguo, you're nothing but a liar.

68
00:04:26,990 --> 00:04:28,320
I didn't lie to you.

69
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:30,730
Haven't I explained everything to you already?

70
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:33,350
What's the point of you constantly harping on this?

71
00:04:33,370 --> 00:04:34,470
Then what are you trying to do

72
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:35,990
by bringing her all the way here?

73
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:38,600
Are you trying to make my life miserable?

74
00:04:38,670 --> 00:04:40,150
How many times do I have to explain?

75
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:42,150
Her mother is sick. Her mother is sick.

76
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,030
She can't take care of her anymore.

77
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:44,030
I'm her father.

78
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:46,090
If I don't take care of her, who will?

79
00:04:46,230 --> 00:04:47,780
You're her father.

80
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:49,370
You can live alone with your daughter.

81
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,590
We divorce.

82
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,480
Get out!

83
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,680
You're too heartless. Divorce then.

84
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:55,830
Han Weiguo.

85
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,740
If you leave now, don't ever come back.

86
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,060
Mom!

87
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:24,310
Why did you throw my clothes?

88
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:27,400
Look, it's all dirty now.

89
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:28,470
I didn't throw it.

90
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:30,980
You did throw it. I saw it myself.

91
00:05:31,010 --> 00:05:32,960
I've said, I didn't throw it.

92
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,250
Come back and apologize to me.

93
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:40,060
Why are you stepping on it? You're so annoying!

94
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:42,150
You're the annoying one! You're the annoying one!

95
00:05:42,210 --> 00:05:44,659
My dad and mom always fight because of you.

96
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:47,159
They never fought before you came.

97
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:50,880
You're annoying! Annoying, annoying, annoying!

98
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:00,870
The other day when my mom was still lucid,

99
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:06,120
[Tomb of late father and mother, Han Weiguo and Ye Min]

100
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,430
she asked me to choose a cemetery for her.

101
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,270
I'll bring her here to take a look.

102
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,730
How is Mrs. Zhou doing?

103
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,510
Just the same.

104
00:06:10,530 --> 00:06:12,490
Sometimes she recognizes people, sometimes she doesn't.

105
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:38,680
[Tomb of late father and mother, Han Weiguo and Ye Min]

106
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:03,110
Dad,

107
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:04,580
Auntie,

108
00:07:05,710 --> 00:07:06,940
we've come to visit you.

109
00:07:09,290 --> 00:07:10,940
We're both doing well.

110
00:07:11,690 --> 00:07:12,690
Don't worry.

111
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,170
Dad has been appearing in my dreams lately.

112
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,660
He's not always smiling like he used to.

113
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,700
I understand what you mean.

114
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:23,160
You want me to take good care of Qing.

115
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:26,520
[Tomb of late father and mother, Han Weiguo and Ye Min]

116
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:24,470
Rest assured,

117
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:26,100
I'm looking after her.

118
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,390
Say a few words to Dad.

119
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:33,070
I...

120
00:07:33,210 --> 00:07:34,590
I don't have much to say.

121
00:07:38,970 --> 00:07:40,570
That's just her temperament.

122
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:42,770
It hasn't changed a bit after all these years.

123
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,409
I'll speak then.

124
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,580
Han Qing is doing well.

125
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:50,270
She's just completely focused on her work

126
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:51,520
and is hardly ever home.

127
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,280
Actually,

128
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:57,220
there's something else I want to tell you.

129
00:07:58,220 --> 00:08:00,280
She's finally found someone she likes.

130
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:02,980
Xueman.

131
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:04,420
He's also a police officer.

132
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:07,650
His name is Zhong Wei.

133
00:08:08,210 --> 00:08:09,540
He's Han Qing's partner.

134
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,400
He got into an accident.

135
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,510
Otherwise, this time,

136
00:08:14,910 --> 00:08:16,620
you might have been able to meet him.

137
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,900
There are some things I've been wanting to tell you too.

138
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,180
I just never had the chance to say them.

139
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:25,430
You've been searching for two whole months.

140
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:28,410
There's no sign of him, dead nor alive.

141
00:08:29,170 --> 00:08:31,430
I don't want to watch you obsess over this every day.

142
00:08:32,070 --> 00:08:33,070
Stop searching.

143
00:08:43,549 --> 00:08:45,190
Actually, after you've passed, Dad,

144
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,920
I've been feeling extremely guilty all these years.

145
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,840
Your family suffered so much,

146
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:52,860
been through so many disasters,

147
00:08:53,430 --> 00:08:54,910
all because of my arrival.

148
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,870
Dad and Auntie got into a car accident while picking me up,

149
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:00,850
and now Zhong Wei has gone missing.

150
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:02,110
It's all because of me.

151
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:04,840
It's all because I appeared in your lives.

152
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:08,010
That's why, Han Qing, I've been desperately trying to be good to you.

153
00:09:08,830 --> 00:09:10,640
I take care of you, clean your room,

154
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:12,790
cook for you, and make soup for you.

155
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,880
I just want to reduce

156
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:15,150
the guilt I feel inside.

157
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,580
Xueman, please stop.

158
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,310
I really can't bear to see you like this.

159
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:20,930
I hope you can look forward.

160
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:23,690
Please stop searching.

161
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:34,590
I'll wait for you in the car.

162
00:10:00,770 --> 00:10:02,430
Dad, stop the car, stop the car!

163
00:10:02,470 --> 00:10:03,700
I want to get out.

164
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:05,560
Be careful.

165
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:06,710
I know.

166
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:11,140
What time is it now?

167
00:10:11,710 --> 00:10:13,150
Go and check on her.

168
00:10:13,230 --> 00:10:14,110
What's the rush?

169
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:15,710
Her sister will be here soon.

170
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:16,770
If you want to go, then go yourself.

171
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:18,510
Han Qing.

172
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,870
Are you done yet?

173
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:23,750
Not yet, it's still early.

174
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:25,140
Are you alright?

175
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:26,660
I'm fine.

176
00:10:26,690 --> 00:10:28,340
How long has it been already?

177
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:31,020
Hurry up, Qing will be here soon.

178
00:10:31,170 --> 00:10:33,500
I know, stop rushing me.

179
00:10:33,540 --> 00:10:36,320
So what if she arrives? What's wrong with waiting a bit?

180
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:38,870
She's your daughter, but Han Qing isn't?

181
00:10:39,310 --> 00:10:41,370
Do we really have to go to a restaurant to welcome her?

182
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,160
Isn't it expensive?

183
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:44,220
I don't take her out more than twice a year.

184
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,160
Han Qing goes there all the time though.

185
00:11:19,050 --> 00:11:20,610
[Police]

186
00:11:29,170 --> 00:11:34,240
[Police]

187
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:31,520
Qing.

188
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:33,850
I've been calling you. Why haven't you answered?

189
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:37,630
Are you in a bad mood?

190
00:11:40,450 --> 00:11:42,160
-Have something sweet.
-Do you need something?

191
00:11:43,530 --> 00:11:45,760
I... I called Zhang Yong to verify.

192
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:47,010
Lyu Jianmin did indeed ask him for a loan,

193
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:47,930
but he didn't lend him any.

194
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,980
Zhang Yong has been in business for years.

195
00:11:49,980 --> 00:11:51,330
He has no bad records.

196
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,580
I also

197
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:54,500
found this at Lyu Jianmin's auto repair shop.

198
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:58,990
[Screenshot of Dongzhou Municipal Public Security Bureau CCTV]

199
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,660
