Location: Lyu Jianmin's repair shop]

200
00:12:00,730 --> 00:12:00,950
[Time: May 10, 2017
Location: Lyu Jianmin's repair shop]

201
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:01,940
Who's in the car?

202
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:03,120
It wasn't captured.

203
00:12:03,230 --> 00:12:04,530
I followed this car the whole way,

204
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,410
and still couldn't get a shot of the driver's face.

205
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:11,210
[Time: May 10, 2017
Location: Lyu Jianmin's repair shop]

206
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:07,770
The most suspicious thing is that,

207
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:09,480
just like the suspect of the dismemberment case,

208
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,060
he kept using the sun visor to cover his face.

209
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:12,350
What about the license plate?

210
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,410
I checked.

211
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,470
It's a real plate,

212
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:16,860
registered under a car rental company.

213
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:20,650
[Name: Li Xiaodong]

214
00:12:17,190 --> 00:12:18,720
The person who rented it is named Li Xiaodong.

215
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,150
He's in the auto parts business.

216
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:24,610
[Mei Shang Tong Car Service]

217
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,390
Are you Li Xiaodong?

218
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,070
Who are you?

219
00:12:35,230 --> 00:12:37,260
We're from the Municipal Criminal Investigation Unit.

220
00:12:42,230 --> 00:12:43,070
What's this about?

221
00:12:45,190 --> 00:12:46,460
We'd like to ask,

222
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:49,200
on the evening of May 10th,

223
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,080
where were you?

224
00:12:50,310 --> 00:12:52,440
On May 10th, I

225
00:12:52,470 --> 00:12:53,430
should have been at the store.

226
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,500
Are you sure?

227
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,110
Let me think.

228
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:59,300
May 10th,

229
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:02,070
Tuesday.

230
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:02,840
Wednesday.

231
00:13:06,010 --> 00:13:07,720
Wednesday.

232
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:12,450
On May 10th, I went to Jingxin.

233
00:13:12,470 --> 00:13:13,940
Here's the toll receipt for the round trip.

234
00:13:13,970 --> 00:13:15,110
You can take a look.

235
00:13:17,410 --> 00:13:18,390
Have a look.

236
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:19,810
Is this you?

237
00:13:23,230 --> 00:13:24,080
Yes, it's me.

238
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,450
Why did you go to Jingxin?

239
00:13:28,490 --> 00:13:29,340
To discuss business.

240
00:13:30,210 --> 00:13:31,420
With whom?

241
00:13:32,070 --> 00:13:32,930
Lyu Jianmin.

242
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,860
A local auto repair shop owner.

243
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,870
Such an important matter as discussing business,

244
00:13:37,890 --> 00:13:39,930
why didn't you remember it earlier?

245
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:43,920
It's not that I didn't remember the business discussion,

246
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:46,020
I just couldn't recall which day did I go.

247
00:13:46,180 --> 00:13:48,310
When did you get to know Lyu Jianmin?

248
00:13:48,350 --> 00:13:49,680
Two years ago, I think.

249
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,350
I know him when

250
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:51,480
he came here to buy parts.

251
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,400
What kind of business did you discuss with him in Jingxin?

252
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,480
He has a batch of old parts

253
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:57,230
that he wants to sell to me for refurbishment.

254
00:13:57,350 --> 00:13:58,630
What kind of old parts?

255
00:13:58,690 --> 00:14:00,520
Do you know the specific car models?

256
00:14:00,570 --> 00:14:02,010
Mainly some

257
00:14:02,050 --> 00:14:02,930
imported car models.

258
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,690
There's Mercedes,

259
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,580
Volvo...

260
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,570
Is there this type?

261
00:14:08,610 --> 00:14:09,550
No.

262
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:09,990
[Screenshot of Dongzhou Municipal Public Security Bureau CCTV]

263
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:11,500
These types aren't worth much at all.

264
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:12,990
On the evening of May 5th,

265
00:14:13,110 --> 00:14:13,940
where were you?

266
00:14:15,470 --> 00:14:17,950
May 5th.

267
00:14:18,470 --> 00:14:20,350
May 5th.

268
00:14:23,410 --> 00:14:25,010
I went to a gathering with friends.

269
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:26,370
We had dinner,

270
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:28,140
then went to a karaoke bar.

271
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:29,660
We partied until 2 or 3 in the morning.

272
00:14:29,830 --> 00:14:31,360
This is the social media post my friend made that day.

273
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:39,120
[Like] [Comment]

274
00:14:37,110 --> 00:14:39,180
Can they all confirm what you just said?

275
